# Per-pack status-line shots are generated by scripts/assets/pack-shot.sh: one positional <text>
# element per glyph (x/y/fill), which no formatter can sort or canonicalize. The render is
# reproducible (the clock is pinned via CCSIDEKICK_NOW), but the files are still machine output —
# mark them generated so reviews collapse them and they stay out of language stats. Do not hand-edit;
# regenerate with `bun run pack:shot packages/packs/<name>`.
packages/packs/*/assets/statusline.svg linguist-generated=true
